changes.comment: UI controls was added for sharing of dashboard with other users
SPI extended with ability for managing of metadata object access permissions
SPI extended with ability for querying of workspace user groups
Workspace user service was extended with ability to query users per page
Workspace dashboard service was extended with ability to query dashboards that are accessible only via link
Workspace dashboard interface was extended with information about share status and access control mode
IListedDashboard interface was extended with “availability” field
